Merge pull request #165 from eventualbuddha/nil-delegate-and-datasource-on-dealloc

Nil out delegate and datasource on dealloc

Add `dealloc` methods to the demos.

This is proper Cocoa etiquette and may help others prevent crashes in
their own apps.

Ensure our own subviews with a delegate are cleaned up.

This can potentially cause a crash if the `linesView` or `dotsView`
were to send a message to its delegate after the delegate was deallocâ€™d.
